<section class="row td-box td-box--primary position-relative td-box--gradient td-box--height-auto">
	<div class="container text-center td-arrow-down">
		<span class="h4 mb-0">
			<p>Navidrome allows you to enjoy your music collection from anywhere, by making it available through a
modern Web UI and through a wide range of third-party compatible mobile apps, for both iOS and Android devices.</p>
<p>Navidrome is open source software distributed <strong>free of charge</strong> under the terms of the
<a href="https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0">GNU GPL v3</a> license.</p>

		</span>
	</div>
</section>





 
