  <div class="mb-4 h1">
    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
  </div>
  <h4 class="h3">Access your music from anywhere!</h4>
  <p class="mb-0"><p>Choose from a large selection of mobile clients or use the integrated web player</p>
</p>
  <p><a href="/docs/overview">Read more …</a></p>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0 text-center ">
  <div class="mb-4 h1">
    <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
  </div>
  <h4 class="h3">Blazing fast!</h4>
  <p class="mb-0"><p>Lightweight, fast and self-contained. Runs well even on resource-limited platforms (ex: Raspberry Pi)</p>
</p>
  <p><a href="/docs/overview">Read more …</a></p>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0 text-center ">
  <div class="mb-4 h1">
    <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
  </div>
  <h4 class="h3">Handles large libraries!</h4>
  <p class="mb-0"><p>Plays well with gigantic music collections (tested with ~900K songs - 2/3 FLAC, 1/3 MP3)</p>
</p>
  <p><a href="/docs/overview">Read more …</a></p>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0 text-center ">
  <div class="mb-4 h1">
    <i class="fas fa-compress-arrows-alt"></i>
  </div>
  <h4 class="h3">Transcoding on the fly!</h4>
  <p class="mb-0"><p>Converts/reduces your music files as you play them, so you don&rsquo;t nuke your data plan</p>
</p>
  <p><a href="/docs/overview">Read more …</a></p>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0 text-center ">
  <div class="mb-4 h1">
    <i class="fas fa-certificate"></i>
  </div>
  <h4 class="h3">Modern and up-to-date</h4>
  <p class="mb-0"><p>Built with new technologies (<a href="https://golang.org">GoLang</a>, <a href="https://reactjs.org">ReactJS</a>, <a href="https://material-ui.com/">Material-UI</a>),
to ensure modern features and compatibility</p>
</p>
  <p><a href="/docs/overview">Read more …</a></p>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0 text-center ">
  <div class="mb-4 h1">
    <i class="fas icon-subsonic"></i>
  </div>
  <h4 class="h3">Subsonic API</h4>
  <p class="mb-0"><p>Compatible with the de facto standard Music API, supporting all its clients and ecosystem</p>
</p>
  <p><a href="/docs/overview/#apps">Read more …</a></p>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0 text-center ">
